properties.text:
[b]Welcome to [color=#ffff00]World Builder[/color]![/b]

[u]Camera movement[/u]
[color=#ffff00]\[WASD][/color] moves the camera.

[u]Operations[/u]
[color=#00ff00]\[Mouse Left][/color] uses the first function of the current tool.
[color=#ff6666]\[Mouse Right][/color] uses the second function of the current tool.
[color=#ffff00]\[Mouse Scroll][/color] increases or decreases the brush size.
[color=#ffff00]\[Left Shift][/color] increases the intensity of the current operation.

[u]Tools[/u]
[color=#ffff00]\[1][/color] selects the [color=#00ff00]Raise[/color] and [color=#ff6666]Sink[/color] tool.
[color=#ffff00]\[2][/color] selects the [color=#00ff00]Smoothen[/color] and [color=#ff6666]Roughen[/color] tool.
[color=#ffff00]\[3][/color] selects the object [color=#00ff00]Placer[/color] and [color=#ff6666]Remover[/color] tool.
[color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color] shows the object picker.

[u]Click anywhere in the screen to lock the mouse.[/u]

Toggle this help message with [color=#ffff00]\[Enter][/color].
